column1: 2/ Slaughter in federally inspected and other plants. Monthly data for 1982 for
cattle, calves, hogs, sheep, and lambs are not official USDA, National Agricultural Statistics Service (NASS)
data but were compiled by USDA, Economic Research Service (ERS).
3/ USDA, NASS data for federally inspected slaughter classes for 1958 to 1970 are supplemented
with USDA, ERS data. Prior to 1986, monthly data for federally inspected beef cow and dairy cow
slaughter are not official USDA, NASS data but were compiled by USDA, ERS.
Source: USDA, National Agricultural Statistics Service, "Livestock Slaughter" and "Poultry Slaughter"
and USDA, ERS calculations for commercial slaughter by class.
